58 And not only do I weep Bolognese here;
59 indeed this place is so full,
60 that so many tongues are not now learned

61 to say ‘yes’ between Savena and Reno;
62 and if of this you want faith or testimony,
63 bring to mind our avaricious breast.

67 I rejoined with my escort;
68 afterward with few steps we became
69 there where a rock from the bank emerged.

70 Quite lightly we climbed that;
71 and turned to the right up its splinter,
72 from those eternal circles we departed.

